code: @Override public void setAsText(@Nullable String text) {     if (text == null) {         setValue(null).     } else {         String value = text.trim().         if (this.charsToDelete != null) {             value = StringUtils.deleteAny(value, this.charsToDelete).         }         if (this.emptyAsNull && "".equals(value)) {             setValue(null).         } else {             setValue(value).         }     } }
@Override public String getAsText() {     Object value = getValue().     return (value != null ? value.toString() : ""). }
